Title

Source: R/mergeData.R
mergeData.Rd

Description

mergeData(x)

Arguments

x

a list

Value

a SummarizedExperiment is returned

Examples

curatedMetagenomicData("AsnicarF_20.+.pathway_abundance", dryrun = FALSE) %>%
    mergeData()
